      "writtenOn": "2016-10-31T14:23:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "No it doesn\u0027t...  Everything is supposed to be tagged though in the new world.\n\nI\u0027ll be sure to skip any color correction in this codec (regardless of the requested dstSpace).  But this does seem a little strange - we\u0027ll be instructing code outside of the codecs to treat this as if it has a real color space.",
      "parentUuid": "e60e367c_46c8b4b1",
      "revId": "e1342b2b3d9ec3bb6865a56eadf2dbcd72c4d538",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "e60e367c_26c3f849",
        "filename": "src/codec/SkWbmpCodec.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 2
      },
      "lineNbr": 108,
      "author": {
        "id": 5010
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-10-31T14:42:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "How awkward is it to have a distinct color space for this? \n\nSkColorSpace::kNone_Named?  kAny_Named?  kMoot_Named?",
      "parentUuid": "86373a0c_47f7fddd",
      "revId": "e1342b2b3d9ec3bb6865a56eadf2dbcd72c4d538",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "86373a0c_2773d995",
        "filename": "src/codec/SkWbmpCodec.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 2
      },
      "lineNbr": 108,
      "author": {
        "id": 5185
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-10-31T14:51:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I thought about this a little bit - I think it is maybe an ok option to have on SkColorSpace.\n\nIt would lead to a significant amount of new code though.  Needs special cases in: Equals, serialize, deserialize, SkColorSpaceXform, gpu pipeline, software pipeling.\n\nSeems like a lot to maintain for something as unimportant as wbmp (unsupported by Chrome, very rare in Android - who treats everything as sRGB anyway).  I think it makes sense to hold onto this idea but not actually implement it until we have a stronger reason to.",
      "parentUuid": "e60e367c_26c3f849",
      "revId": "e1342b2b3d9ec3bb6865a56eadf2dbcd72c4d538",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "e60e367c_06afdc81",
        "filename": "src/codec/SkWbmpCodec.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 2
